<ul>
<li>* indicates that the other pronunciation is also current in RP.</li>
<li>** indicates that this word had late Middle English <span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">/au/</span> (possibly in addition to late Middle English <span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">/a/</span>)</li>
