</tr>
<tr>
<td>_<span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">[ŋk]</span></td>
<td>bank ("bench", "financial institution"), canker, flank, plank, ranco(u)r, sanctity</td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
