<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Phonological_history_of_English_short_A&action=edit&section=23.php.html" title="Edit section: æ-tensing">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id=".C3.A6-tensing"><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">æ</span>-tensing</span></h3>
<ul>
<li>Benua, L. 1995. Identity effects in <a href="Morphology_(linguistics)" title="Morphology (linguistics)">morphological</a> truncation. In <i>Papers in <a href="Optimality_theory" title="Optimality theory">optimality theory</a></i>, ed. J. N. Beckman, L. Walsh Dickey, and S. Urbanczyk. <a href="University_of_Massachusetts_Amherst" title="University of Massachusetts Amherst">UMass</a> Occasional Papers 18. <a href="Amherst,_Massachusetts" title="Amherst, Massachusetts">Amherst</a>: GLSA, 77–136.</li>
